OL,3,CBritish Superbikes rider in 'serious'
OL,4,Ccondition after Donington Park crash
OL,6,F"He and his machine then collided with
OL,7,FNathan Harrison who also fell.
OL,9,F"The race was immediately red flagged
OL,10,Fand both riders were attended to by
OL,11,Fthe BSB Medical Team.
OL,13,F"Callum Grigor was found to be in a
OL,14,Fserious condition and required
OL,15,Fimmediate trackside intervention,
OL,16,Fincluding being placed into an induced
OL,17,Fcoma.
OL,19,F"Nathan Harrison was treated at the
OL,20,Fmedical centre for an isolated limb
OL,21,Finjury.
